\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\noindent

\emph on
Dirichlet process concentration parameter (
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha_{0}$
\end_inset

):
\emph default

\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
[\alpha_{0}|\cdot] & \propto & \text{Gamma}(r+H-1,q-\sum_{h=1}^{H-1}\log(1-v_{h})).
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

See page 553 in Gelman et al.
 (2014) for this full conditional.
\emph on

\begin_inset VSpace bigskip
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\noindent

\emph on
Error in the observation process (
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

):
\emph default

\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
[\sigma|\cdot] & \propto & \prod_{t=1}^{T}[\mathbf{s}_{t}|\boldsymbol{\mu}_{0,h},\sigma^{2}][\sigma]
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

The update for 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

 proceeds using Metropolis-Hastings.
 
\end_layout

